story: Pwnky, a creature from the Space of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Yellow eyes  eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Mechanic mouth  mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Ears bow ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Hidden hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Black hat hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Glasses, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Space, Yellow eyes , Mechanic body, Mechanic mouth , Ears bow, Hidden hair, Black hat, Glasses
